        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR3j0010-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_007-8a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T16:59:15.881+09:00">不和外物相混杂，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_007-8a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T16:59:37.939+09:00">而天下自然服从于德。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_007-10a.125" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T17:03:26.345+09:00">如能看轻天下的权势，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_007-10a.126" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T17:03:35.31+09:00">那么精神便不会受到外物的牵累；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_007-10a.127" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T17:05:16.091+09:00">把世间万物看作小事，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_007-10a.128" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T17:05:19.301+09:00">那么心灵便不会受到诱惑了；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_007-11a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T17:12:34.017+09:00">这就是看轻天子权势的事例。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_007-11a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T17:13:52.319+09:00">因此把天子之位禅让给舜，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_007-11a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T17:14:03.368+09:00">就像解除了沉重的负担，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_007-13a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T17:38:20.793+09:00">天子的权势是最大的了</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_007-13a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T17:38:39.2+09:00">而尧却把它传给他人；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_007-14a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T18:12:39.561+09:00">那么让他左手执掌天下的图籍，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_007-14a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T18:14:30.484+09:00">没有天下的权力对自己性情没有损害，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_007-14a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T18:15:21.791+09:00">有了天子之位不超过自己合适的要求，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_007-15a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T18:18:20.61+09:00">就不必用天下的权势来惑乱；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_007-15a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T18:18:17.226+09:00">懂得了养生的要道</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_007-15a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T18:18:47.228+09:00">了解了未生时候的快乐，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_007-15a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T18:18:50.843+09:00">便不能用死亡未相威吓；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_009-48a.121" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T20:30:09.306+09:00">凡是将要在天下树立德行和意旨，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_010-40a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T20:37:22.205+09:00">天下的任何人都不能遏止和强夺。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_010-78a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T20:39:34.124+09:00">果真能够爱护而使他们有利，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_010-78a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T20:39:49.253+09:00">便可以让天下之人依从了。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_012-15a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T21:06:46.689+09:00">陈说治理天下的道理。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_012-48a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T21:56:27.931+09:00">秦始皇取得天下，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_012-57a.44" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T22:32:31.35+09:00">可以长久地持守天下而不会失去。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_013-17a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T23:38:50.809+09:00">那么天下的人讨伐我就困难了。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_013-17a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T23:38:59.357+09:00">假使我有暴乱的行为，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_013-21a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T23:43:40.612+09:00">因此在天下舒展开未而没有间隙，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_013-21a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T23:43:58.986+09:00">研究时势变化而根据它行事，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_013-21a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-03T23:44:18.162+09:00">权衡事情大小而依据它谋划。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_013-34a.32" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T15:50:16.091+09:00">禹力天下辛劳治水</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_013-34a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T15:50:17.221+09:00">而死后托为土地神；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_014-18a.68" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T17:13:22.279+09:00">天下的人都随波逐流，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_014-20a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T17:15:26.913+09:00">因此功劳覆盖天下，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_014-20a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T17:18:33.448+09:00">也不施舍他的美德；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_014-23a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T17:20:03.802+09:00">天下并不是没有讲究信誉之人．</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_014-23a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T17:21:34.546+09:00">天下不是没有清廉之士，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_014-30a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T17:23:59.458+09:00">天下的万物是广博的而智术是肤浅的，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_014-33a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T17:26:13.23+09:00">因此天下能够得到而不可强取，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_014-33a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T17:26:27.834+09:00">霸王可以接受而不可以强求。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_014-33a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T17:31:03.23+09:00">诸侯不加防备，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_014-33a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T17:31:06.445+09:00">那么天下贤人可以乘机而起。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_014-36a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T17:37:18.032+09:00">能够不因为天下之利伤害他的国家，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_014-36a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T17:38:01.159+09:00">而又不因为国家之利伤害他的身体的人，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_014-43a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T17:43:16.1+09:00">贤君用一个人的力量而能兼治天下，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_014-48a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T17:51:06.472+09:00">即使用天地这样大的地方，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_014-48a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T17:50:56.386+09:00">也不能换取他的一概之量；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_014-57a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T17:58:47.214+09:00">所以不要说我没有什么办法做到因为天下的事情很遥远．</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_014-57a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T17:57:55.891+09:00">也不要说我不想达到目标因为天下之事不能到来。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_014-58a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T18:05:05.313+09:00">名位利益充满天下，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_014-58a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T18:05:12.349+09:00">却不能够动摇他的意志。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_015-1a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T18:09:52.971+09:00">贪财昧利凶狠残暴之人．</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_015-1a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T18:10:03.275+09:00">残害天下．</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_015-1a.31" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T18:11:02.306+09:00">使万人骚动，没有办法使他们安居。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_015-2a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T18:14:03.058+09:00">耗尽天下的资财．</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_015-8a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T18:24:11.493+09:00">顺应大道而行动，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_015-8a.31" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T18:24:16.361+09:00">天下人民会因此而响应；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_015-8a.32" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T18:24:28.131+09:00">按照人民的意愿而考虑行事，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_015-8a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T18:24:32.175+09:00">天下之人会为之而战斗。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_015-11a.40" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T18:31:00.031+09:00">土地辽阔人口众多，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_015-11a.41" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T18:31:21.966+09:00">几乎平分天下，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_015-11a.78" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T18:36:26.945+09:00">天下人民像焦烤灼热一样饱受煎熬，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_015-12a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T19:56:18.002+09:00">利刃没有全部拔出来，而天下就荻得了。  傅：得： 北宋本原作“传＂。刘绩《补庄》本作“得＂。据正。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_015-14a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T20:03:46.345+09:00">凡是具有形体的．</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_015-14a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T20:04:52.478+09:00">天下人都能看得到；　　讼： 公。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_015-21a.39" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T20:32:56.695+09:00">即使突然在天下交兵，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_015-21a.40" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T20:32:57.132+09:00">又有谁敢于凌驾在他们之上呢？</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_016-19a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T20:38:47.958+09:00">侯王重视它，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_016-19a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T20:39:03.254+09:00">用来作为天下平正的标准。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_018-58a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T21:03:20.435+09:00">必定是天下很勇敢的人了，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_019-3a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T21:10:11.224+09:00">為的是天下有强大的压迫弱小的．</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_019-3a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T21:10:14.894+09:00">众多的欺凌人少的：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_019-23a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T21:22:42.684+09:00">现在都把毛墙、西施看作天下的美人．</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_020-8a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T22:21:29.352+09:00">四每之内． 没有人不仰慕国君的恩德．</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_020-8a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T22:21:38.775+09:00">依顺君主的意旨，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_020-8a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T22:22:04.775+09:00"> 东夷北狄等远方之国，经过多次翻译而来到中央之国。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_020-8a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T22:22:31.717+09:00">这不是靠向家家户户辩白说明，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_020-8a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T22:22:51.261+09:00">而是把他的真诚之心．</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_020-8a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T22:23:38.286+09:00">施行天下罢了。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_020-11a.50" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T22:34:06.606+09:00">于是在他所统领的范围内．</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_020-11a.51" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T22:35:02.228+09:00">命令四方长官推荐哪怕低贱之人代他统领天下。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_020-11a.59" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T22:41:39.76+09:00">于是尧把自己的九个儿子囑託给舜，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_020-11a.60" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T22:41:48.849+09:00">又赠给他昭华美王．</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_020-11a.61" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T22:42:04.853+09:00">并把天下传给了他。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_020-22a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T22:58:32.474+09:00">因此臧武仲凭借着他的智慧保存了鲁国，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_020-22a.34" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T22:58:42.984+09:00">而天下诸侯没有人能使鲁灭亡；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_020-24a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T23:05:35.492+09:00">因此举用天下的高才， 任为天子三公；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_020-28a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-04T23:38:20.752+09:00">假使有人左手拿着占有天下的地图而右手用剑去割他的咽喉．</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_020-30a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-05T00:07:26.467+09:00">调节自身都不能做到，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_020-30a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-05T00:07:46.546+09:00"> 治理天下又怎么能办到呢？</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3j0010_tls_020-31a.39" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-05T00:13:32.443+09:00">使官员身插笏板接受天下朝拜。</seg>
                </p>
